          "bodySize": 1749,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1749,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_0154y5FrajE3ZyXSvAXPpdoY\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"<thinking>\\nThe user wants me to test reasoning tokens. This seems like a request to demonstrate or test my ability to use internal reasoning/thinking before providing a response.\\n\\nLet me think through what this might mean:\\n1. They want to see if I can show my reasoning process\\n2. They want to test if reasoning tokens are working/visible\\n3. They want me to demonstrate problem-solving with visible thought process\\n\\nI'll provide a response that demonstrates reasoning and explains what reasoning tokens are in this context.\\n</thinking>\\n\\nI can help you test reasoning tokens! \\n\\n**What I understand:** You want to see my internal reasoning process before I give my final answer.\\n\\n**Let me demonstrate with a simple problem:**\\n\\nIf I'm asked: \\\"How many Rs are in the word STRAWBERRY?\\\"\\n\\nMy reasoning would be:\\n- Let me go through each letter: S-T-R-A-W-B-E-R-R-Y\\n- S: not an R\\n- T: not an R\\n- R: this is an R (1st R)\\n- A: not an R\\n- W: not an R\\n- B: not an R\\n- E: not an R\\n- R: this is an R (2nd R)\\n- R: this is an R (3rd R)\\n- Y: not an R\\n\\n**Answer:** There are 3 Rs in STRAWBERRY.\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Is there a specific problem or question you'd like me to reason through?** I can show my thinking process for:\\n- Math problems\\n- Logic puzzles\\n- Word problems\\n- Analysis tasks\\n- Or anything else you'd like to test!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":10,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":366,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
